  <Overview>
    <Title>Describe Your Surroundings</Title>
    <Text>
      For five minutes, please describe the room you are in right now. Record your observations as an audio file and upload it using the field below.

     <Text>Please upload your audio file here.</Text>

   <AnswerSpecification>
     <FileUploadAnswer>
      <MaxFileSizeInBytes>300000000</MaxFileSizeInBytes>
      <MinFileSizeInBytes>1000</MinFileSizeInBytes>
    </FileUploadAnswer>
   </AnswerSpecification>
  </Question>
</QuestionForm>
